commit.message:
gsocket.h: On Windows...

2008-08-08  Thomas Quinot  <quinot@adacore.com>

	* gsocket.h:
	On Windows, include <errno.h> and redefine only selected errno values
	from their <winsock2.h> definitions.

From-SVN: r138874

files.patch:
@@ -60,6 +60,7 @@
 #endif

 #if defined(__vxworks)
